    "lyricsHtml": "\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#6\">F#6</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Lá, lá, lá, lá, lá, lá, lá</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#6\">F#6</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Lá, lá, lá, lá, lá, lá, lá</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#\">F#</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Quando a gente tá contente</span>\n                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>                       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Tanto faz o quente, tanto faz o frio, tanto faz</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#\">F#</span>                               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que eu me esqueça do meu compromisso</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>                              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#4/7\">C#4/7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Com isso ou aquilo que aconteceu dez minutos atrás</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#\">F#</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Dez minutos atrás de uma idéia já dão</span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Pra uma teia de aranha crescer e prender</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#\">F#</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Sua vida na cadeia do pensamento</span>\n             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#4/7\">C#4/7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que de um momento pro outro começa a doer</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Quando a gente tá contente</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Gente é gente (gato é gato!)</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Barata pode ser um barato total</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Tudo que você disser deve fazer bem</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Ab7\">Ab7</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Nada que você comer deve fazer mal</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Quando a gente tá contente</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Nem pensar que está contente</span>\n                                      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B7\">B7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Nem pensar que está contente a gente quer</span>\n                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Nem pensar a gente quer, a gente quer</span>\n                       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Ab7\">Ab7</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#7\">C#7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">A gente quer, a gente quer é viver</span>\n",
